SUMMARY:CAMPGround26 Concert 1
LOCATION:1624 E 7th Ave Tampa \, FL 33605 United States
DESCRIPTION:CAMPGround26\, an international new music festival\, takes ove
 r Tampa\, FL\, March 57! Expect multiple world premieres\, three brand-new
  monodramas\, and a special house installation projectall packed into an u
 nforgettable first week of March. Dont miss this one-of-a-kind musical adv
 enture! CAMPGround26 launches with an exciting opening night featuring thr
 ee new monodramas by Mojan Alaiyeh\, Parastoo Shafiei\, and Negar Soleyman
 ifar\, written especially for soprano Jamie Jordan and the CAMP ensemble. 
 The evening also showcases an immersive installation and a dynamic ensembl
 e work with electronics by Zouning Liao\, setting the stage for a bold and
  adventurous festival opening. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/1
 85886
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.tampa.gov/node/185886
END:VEVENT
