SUMMARY:The 2-mile Mission
LOCATION:333 S Franklin St | Channel Entry Tampa \, FL 33602 United States
DESCRIPTION:Join The 2-Mile Mission powered by North Star Therapy\, a comm
 unity charity walk to raise awareness for mental health and support the li
 fe-saving work of the Crisis Center of Tampa Bay. A suggested 15 registrat
 ion donation helps fund critical care and support services. After the walk
 \, join us at 1983 for refreshments and connection. Everyone is welcome! R
 egister now: https:therapyintampa.comregistration (https:therapyintampa.co
 mregistration) \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/185731
