 in oil from the live model. First\, well cover the basics of color theory 
 and paint mixing. Participants will then map out their study with an under
 -drawing\, before building up the painting with a direct\, or alla prima t
 echnique. Through demonstration and individual critiques\, students will g
 ain confidence in handling oils and develop an understanding of how to cap
 ture a likeness. \n\nPermalink: https://www.tampa.gov/node/177336
